{
  "texts": [
    "Plant Reactome, as another example, serves as an expansive knowledgebase of plant pathways, offering curated pathways from rice and projections to 129 other species.",
    "Its repository of 339 reference pathways provides a detailed view of metabolic processes, hormone signaling, and genetic regulation (Gupta et al., 2024).",
    "By facilitating the visualization and analysis of multi-omics data within plant pathways, this resource allows breeders to identify genetic interactions and pathways critical for desired traits such as enhanced yield or stress tolerance, directing breeding efforts more effectively.",
    "As another example, WGIE specializes in extracting important wheat germplasm information from fragmented research data (Wei and Fan, 2024).",
    "By employing conversational LLMs and innovative data extraction methodologies, WGIE enhances the accessibility and efficiency of identifying useful wheat traits."
  ]
}